This paper is about exploration strategies for mobile robots, which is a core functionality in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning method for exploration, which involves both artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method uses depth information from an RGB-D sensor, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the cognitive ability of the robot controller, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY).
